<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Lesson 5 - Text Styles</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial;
      background-color: #111;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .box {
      background: white;
      color: black;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 15px 0;
      width: 300px;
    }
    .tahoma {
      font-family: Tahoma;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 20px;
    }
    .arial-title {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .sale {
      color: red;
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .course-title {
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    .level {
      color: gray;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .desc {
      font-size: 14px;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    .btn {
      background-color: green;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      padding: 8px 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .business-title {
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    .link {
      color: blue;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .apple {
      text-align: center;
    }
    .new {
      color: orange;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .product {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .price {
      color: gray;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .buy {
      background-color: blue;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      padding: 8px 15px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .stock-price {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .usd {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: gray;
    }
    .up {
      color: green;
    }
    .down {
      color: red;
    }
    .tweet {
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .username {
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .tag {
      color: gray;
    }
    .mention {
      color: blue;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="box tahoma">
    This is Tahoma Font
  </div>
  <div class="box">
    <div class="arial-title">Biggest Deals of the Year!</div>
    <div class="sale">Sales end Tuesday</div>
  </div>
  <div class="box">
    <div class="course-title">HTML CSS Course</div>
    <div class="level">Beginner to Pro</div>
    <div class="desc">
      In this course, we'll learn the skills you need to become a developer.
    </div>
    <button class="btn">Get Started</button>
  </div>
  <div class="box">
    <div class="business-title">Shopping for your business?</div>
    <p>See how Apple at Work can help.</p>
    <span class="link">Learn more ></span>
  </div>
  <div class="box apple">
    <div class="new">New</div>
    <div class="product">MacBook Pro</div>
    <div class="product">Supercharged for pros.</div>
    <div class="price">From $1999</div>
    <button class="buy">Buy</button>
  </div>
  <div class="box">
    <div class="stock-price">
      1,049.61 <span class="usd">USD</span>
    </div>
    <div class="up">+18.05 (1.75%) today</div>
    <div class="down">After hours 1,048.00 -1.61 (0.15%)</div>
  </div>
  <div class="box tweet">
    <span class="username">freeCodeCamp.org</span>
    <span class="tag">@freeCodeCamp · 1h</span>
    <p>
      As a web developer, you'll want to make your projects easy to use and navigate around.
    </p>
    <p>
      Here <span class="mention">@chp_it</span> outlines the top skills new developers should have.
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
